query:
-- Check coverage
SELECT 'Coverage' as type, countryCode, NULL as serviceType, NULL as serviceLevel, NULL as rate
FROM supplierCoverageCountries 
WHERE supplierId = 240001 AND countryCode = 'AU'

UNION ALL

-- Check rates
SELECT 'Rate' as type, countryCode, serviceType, serviceLevel, rateUsdCents as rate
FROM supplierRates 
WHERE supplierId = 240001 
  AND countryCode = 'AU'
  AND isServiceable = 1;
